<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.9.2">
<l>eṉṟuko ṟōḻimīrkā ḷemmainīrnalin teṉceytīrō</l>
<l>poṉṟikaḻ puṉṉaimakiḻ putumātavi mītaṇavi</l>
<l>teṉṟaṉ maṇaṅkamaḻun tiruvalla vāḻnakaru</l>
<l>ṇiṉṟapi rāṉaṭinī ṟaṭiyōṅkoṇṭu cūṭuvatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When, friends, – what will you do, afflicting us? –</l>
<l>will there be taking [and] wearing, for us who [are his] servants, the ash from the feet of the lord who stands</l>
<l>in the city of Tiruvallavāḻ, where the south wind clings to the tops</l>
<l>of gold-glittering mastwood, Makiḻ [and] Mātavi [and] spreads the scent?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
